[10.025144, "o", "fast-agent is accessing the OS keyring for stored tokens. Some platforms may\r\npause and show a prompt. (loading Codex OAuth tokens)\r\nUse '/' for commands, '!' for shell. '#' to query, '@' to switch agents\r\nCTRL+T multiline, CTRL+Y copy last message, CTRL+E external editor.\r\nCTRL+Space or Tab for path completion. Use /attach, `^file:`, or `^url:` for\r\nattachments. F10 to clear.\r\nfast-agent environment ~/source/fast-agent-pr/.cdx (2 agents, 2 hooks, 8\r\nextensions, 2 modelrefs) via cli\r\n\r\n▎▶ a2a_remote ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\nplease stream\r\n\r\n▎◀ a2a_remote A2A\r\nstream chunk one\r\nstream chunk two\r\n\r\n▎▶ a2a_remote ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\nrespond with files\r\n\r\n▎◀ a2a_remote A2A\r\nfile response report.pdf (application/pdf)\r\n\r\n{\r\n  \"ok\": true,\r\n  \"source\": \"fake-a2a-server\"\r\n}\r\n\r\n[note.txt: 3 bytes text/plain]\r\n\r\n❯\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n  a2a_remote[A2A]    ▲  fast-agent fake A2A serv… | 002 |  NRML  | fast-agent 0.\r\n"]
